{"tid":1931543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法官下令港鐵披露8.31太子站片段","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T09:00:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7ef61c994b67084b851bf8e274f75ba44235ad","tid":1931543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/03/18/2406808_1b0e1a48e519cd08fa7f9d84f1b89811.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2F2406808_1b0e1a48e519cd08fa7f9d84f1b89811.jpeg&h=f85d8369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(無綫新聞截圖)<br />\n<br />\n在8.31太子站衝突中被捕獲釋的教育大學學生會長梁耀霆，入稟高等法院要求港鐵披露當晚的閉路電視片段，以助進行申索，案件今午在高等法院頒布判詞。<br />\n<br />\n法官周家明下令港鐵須在7日內向原告交出‪8月31日晚上10時45分‬至翌日‪凌晨1時30分‬在太子站的閉路電視片段，以及‪9月1日凌晨1時25分至2時‬在荔枝角站的閉路電視片段。<br />\n<br />\n去年8月31日晚上，警方防暴警察及速龍小隊衝入港鐵太子站月台及列車展開拘捕行動，並發生警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2406808/%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B28.31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2406808%2F%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B28.31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=e45c5a49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2406808/%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B28.31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5</a>"},{"pid":"abd164194bedc0281857026f13806c00ad38626b","tid":1931543,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 